reviewText:
It was not "Queen live in Mexico"
But a "Queen Live in Budapest" copy
THIS IS A BUDAPEST CONCERT...IN A BAD QUALITY, YOU SAY EXCLUSIVE DVD...BUT THIS IS NOT THE REAL CONCERT IN MEXICO.
This is actually "Queen Live in Budapest '86" while the title of the product is misleading Queen's fan that this is another rare Queen live exclusive DVD!!!  It's a kind of "cheating" magic!!!!
